Warzyn Pierwszy  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Nagłowice, within Jędrzejów County, Świętokrzyskie Voivodeship, in south-central Poland. It lies approximately  south-east of Nagłowice,  west of Jędrzejów, and  south-west of the regional capital Kielce.
